data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF & available under appraisal value of $163,000! The seller has only improved the property since the previous buyer couldn't perform so you're in luck! 3 beds & 3 bathrooms. As you enter through the inviting front foyer, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that flow seamlessly through the living and formal dining spaces. The living room boasts a stunning brick fireplace and built-in shelving, adding warmth and character to the home. The main level features a primary bedroom with a 3/4 en-suite bath. The kitchen is equipped with sleek stainless steel appliances, enhancing both style and functionality. Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms and a 3/4 bath, while the basement offers another 3/4 bath and extra living space. The house also benefits from a recent deck facelift, ensuring you can enjoy outdoor living to the fullest. Recent updates include a HE Furnace and Water Heater. The property includes a two-stall garage, offering ample parking and storage!
